Different types of years/synodic cycles

Metonic 19 years
       235 synodic months
Hence, 254 zodiacal months
Days in cycle = 6940

Oktaeteris
       8 years
       99 months
Hence,
       107 zodiacal months
Unknown number of days
Set default as 2922 days (365 1/4 days per year)

